    "This fusion of data not only increases the accuracy of disease detection but also provides valuable insights obtained from different types of diagnostic tests.",
    "It also aids in establishing the correlations among the tests (Kong et al. 2022).",
    "Although extensive investigations have been conducted on contriving ML models for AD diagnosis, there is still a clear gap in employing multimodal data as evident from the literature review presented in Sect. 3.3.",
    "We discuss the challenges and future directions with respect to multimodal data in further sections.",
    "While in multimodal data, we considered data from different modalities i.e., different diagnostic tests, in hybrid data there is a combination of different diagnostic data from same modality."
